Text:
Classification: Documentary
Genre: Crime
Status: New Series
Network: BBC THREE ( United Kingdom)
Airs: Fridays at 08:30 pm
Runtime: 30 Minutes
Premiere: February 04, 2011

The Lock Up is a documentary series which has access to the custody suite of Humberside Police, which specialises in hosting Hull's 2,000 young people who are arrested each year.

(http://www.tvrage.com/The_Lock_Up_UK)
